quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  44,40,Achiika! Saliya karibu dali n-nyɛ bɛ daalikauli saha namgbaniyini
  44,41,"Dabsi’ shεli dɔɣim ni ti ku tooi niŋ dɔɣim anfaani shεli, bɛ mi pala bɛ ni yɛn sɔŋ shɛba"
  44,42,"Naɣila Naawuni ni zo so nambɔɣu. Achiika! Ŋuna n-nyɛ Nyɛŋda, Zaadali Nambɔzobonaa"
  44,43,Achiika! Ma a nya Zakkuumi tia
  44,44,Di nyɛla tuumbe tumda bindirigu
  44,45,"Ka di ŋmani kpatulli (bee tahiʒɛɣu din nyɛlgi), ka kpeeri puya ni"
  44,46,Kamani kotulum ni yi kpeeri shεm
  44,47,"(Ka Naawuni yεli Malaaikanima): “Gbaami ya o (chεfura), ka tɔhigi o n-ti niŋ ʒehiimi buɣum sunsuuni.”"
  44,48,"“Di nyaaŋa, kpaami ya kotulum m-pa o zuɣu ni, ka di nyɛ azaaba n-ti o.”"
  44,49,"(Ka bɛ yεli chεfura): “Lammi (azaaba). Achiika! A nyɛla ŋun daa nyɛŋ, ka daa mali jilma (Dunia puuni)"
  44,50,Achiika! Ŋɔ maa n-nyɛ yi (chεfur- nim’) ni daa zilsiri shεli maa
  44,51,Achiika! Wuntizɔriba yɛn ti be la suhudoo shee
  44,52,Alizanda yiya mini bilsi puuni
  44,53,"Ka bɛ yɛri silki falafala, ni silki din timsa, ka nyɛla ban nina kpa taba"
  44,54,"Lala n-nyɛ li, ka Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) yɛn ti laɣim ba ni (Alizanda) paɣa shεba ban nimbihi vεla, ka lahi nyɛ niŋkara"
  44,55,"Ka bɛ boonda ni bɛ ti ba binwolli balibu kam, ka nyɛ ban mali yɛmbahiga"
  44,56,"Bɛ ti bi yɛn lam kpibu di (Alizanda maa) puuni, naɣila bɛ tuuli kpibu (Dunia puuni) la, ka O (Naawuni) lahi gu ba ka chɛ ʒɛhiimi buɣum daazaaba"
  44,57,"Ka di nyɛ tibginsim din yi a Duuma (Naawuni) sani na, dina n-nyɛ tarli din galsi"
  44,58,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Achiika! Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) balgi li (Alkur’aani) mi a zilli zuɣu, domin bɛ (Larbunim’) zaŋ li n-teei Naawunim yɛla"
  44,59,"Dinzuɣu, ʒiya guhimi ba (ka nya din yɛn ti paai ba), achiika! Bɛ gba nyɛla ban ʒiya guhira"